#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.setdiff1d.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.setdiff1d"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:1 of
msgid "Find the set difference of two tensors."
msgstr "找出两个张量的集合差集。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:3 of
msgid "Return the unique values in `ar1` that are not in `ar2`."
msgstr "返回在 `ar1` 中但不在 `ar2` 中的唯一值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:5 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:7 of
msgid "Input comparison tensor."
msgstr "输入比较张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:9 of
msgid ""
"If True, the input tensors are both assumed to be unique, which can speed"
" up the calculation.  Default is False."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则假定输入张量中的元素都是唯一的，这可以加速计算。默认值为 "
"False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d:13 of
msgid ""
"**setdiff1d** -- 1D tensor of values in `ar1` that are not in `ar2`. The "
"result is sorted when `assume_unique=False`, but otherwise only sorted if"
" the input is sorted."
msgstr ""
"**setdiff1d** -- 一个一维张量，包含在 `ar1` 中但不在 `ar2` 中的值。当 `"
"assume_unique=False` 时，结果是排序的；否则仅在输入已排序时结果才是排序的"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.setdiff1d.setdiff1d of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

